Package: SoloGEx
Type: Package
Title: Solo Gene Expression Explorer for Hypothesis Generation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Stefan", "Lang", email = "stefan.lang@med.lu.se", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    SoloGEx provides a minimal R framework to explore single-sample gene expression data 
    against a reference dataset. It calculates per-group statistics, compares singleton 
    samples, and generates hypothesis-driven insights. Designed for pilot studies and 
    rapid exploratory analysis.
